flowchart TD
    A[公理A] --> Base[Base结构]
    B[公理B] --> Base
    C[公理C] --> Base
    Base --> WellFounded[颜色类良基性]
    Base --> Typical[典型性定理]
    Typical --> Global[全局一致性]
    Base --> Hilbert[希尔伯特赋值]
    Hilbert --> Linear[线性算子]
    Linear --> Tensor[张量积]
    Tensor --> Regge[Regge演算]
    Regge --> Convergence[收敛性]